<tool_call>file_operations_writer
{
  "destination": "test_input.csv",
  "data": {"headers": ["sample", "value", "valid"], "rows": [["test1", 1, true], ["test2", 2, false]]},
  "options": {"format": "csv"}
}
</tool_call>

Now that we have successfully created the input file, I'll proceed with reading it using the file_operations_reader tool.

